
'''朝鲜网络行动 <ref>{{Cite book|last=Ziccardi|first=Giovanni|title=Resistance, Liberation Technology and Human Rights in the Digital Age|publisher=Springer Science & Business Media|isbn=9789400752764|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=cojY3Xk7aQwC&pg=PA301|accessdate=22 April 2017|language=en|date=2012-09-28}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite book|last=Abbott|first=Jason|title=The Political Economy of the Internet in Asia and the Pacific: Digital Divides, Economic Competitiveness, and Security Challenges|publisher=Praeger|isbn=9780275980214|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=K8bZAAAAMAAJ|accessdate=22 April 2017|language=en|date=2004-01-01}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=The Transformation of Cyberactivism and Democratic Governance in Korea: The Role of Technology, Civil Society, and Institutions|url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/290730659|accessdate=22 April 2017|language=en}}</ref>'''是指利用[[信息技术|信息技术]]（例如[[網絡行動主義|因特网]]）和[[公民社会|民间]]（一般在朝鲜境外）分发信息<ref>{{Cite book|last=Kim|first=Hyuk-Rae|last2=Kim|first2=Hyŏng-nae|title=State-centric to Contested Social Governance in Korea: Shifting Power|publisher=Routledge|isbn=9780415587457|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=o6cy1If7948C&pg=PA201|accessdate=22 April 2017|language=en|year=2013}}</ref>以支持朝鲜改革而进行的[[網絡行動主義|行动]]。

== 措施 ==

* 向朝鲜[[走私|走私]]国外的媒体，信息或技术；
* 利用本地IT基础架构；
* 构建本地IT基础架构（例如[[网状网络|网状网络]]）。

== 用例 ==

* 由脱北者[[朴尚學|朴尚学]]领导的一个维权团体“[[自由北韓運動聯盟|自由北韓運動聯盟]]”，将反朝鲜传单，美元和[[闪存盘|闪存盘]]通过氦气球散布到朝鲜各地；<ref>{{Cite web|title=North Korean defector-activists step up propaganda war|url=https://www.ft.com/content/5d7e8fa0-6902-11e6-a0b1-d87a9fea034f|accessdate=22 April 2017|publisher=Financial Times|archive-date=2019-02-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190207065200/https://www.ft.com/content/5d7e8fa0-6902-11e6-a0b1-d87a9fea034f|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=The people flying balloons to North Korea|url=http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20150605-the-group-flying-tech-filled-balloons-to-north-korea|accessdate=22 April 2017|archive-date=2018-05-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180525183332/http://www.bbc.com/future/story/20150605-the-group-flying-tech-filled-balloons-to-north-korea|dead-url=no}}</ref>
* 根据No Chain小组的创始人[[鄭光日|郑光日]]的说法，自2015年初以来，有[[無人航空載具|无人机]]一直向朝鲜居民提供[[SD卡|SD卡]]和[[随身碟|闪存驱动器]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=Activists are using drones to rain flash drives full of TV shows on North Korea|url=http://www.digitaltrends.com/cool-tech/north-korea-drone-usb/|accessdate=22 April 2017|date=26 May 2016|publisher=Digital Trends|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029174039/https://www.digitaltrends.com/cool-tech/north-korea-drone-usb/|dead-url=no}}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web|title=Activists: Drones drop forbidden media into N. Korea|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/25/asia/north-korea-drones/|accessdate=22 April 2017|author=Park|first=Madison|publisher=CNN|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112323/https://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/25/asia/north-korea-drones/|dead-url=no}}</ref>；
